About Dhindhali

According to Census 2011 information the location code or village code of Dhindhali village is 110498. Dhindhali village is located in Kairana tehsil of Muzaffarnagar district in Uttar Pradesh, India. It is situated 18km away from sub-district headquarter Kairana (tehsildar office) and 56km away from district headquarter Muzaffarnagar. As per 2009 stats, Dhindhali village is also a gram panchayat.

The total geographical area of village is 403.33 hectares. Dhindhali has a total population of 2,458 peoples, out of which male population is 1,323 while female population is 1,135. Literacy rate of dhindhali village is 58.01% out of which 67.04% males and 47.49% females are literate. There are about 433 houses in dhindhali village. Pincode of dhindhali village locality is 247778.

Un is nearest town to dhindhali for all major economic activities, which is approximately 1km away.
